learning_outcomes.en:
Student who has passed the course: 
* has a systematic knowledge of the specificity of the development of the Russian literature during the mid-19th century;
* has a knowledge about the creations by Russian poets, playwrights, and prose writers of the mid-19th century.
* is able to bring out and analyze the specifics of the social-psychological novel of the mid-19th century; 
* is able to describe the aesthetic and ideological features of the poetry of the mid-19th century, i.e. the period of 1850s-1870.
